<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,387,151,176]" italics="true" pageId="153" pageNumber="154">Leuconia glomerosa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation box="[393,602,151,176]" pageId="153" pageNumber="154" refId="ref64318" refString="Bowerbank, J. S. (1873) Contributions to a General History of the Spongiadae. Part IV. Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London, 1873, 3 - 25. Available from: https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / item / 90422  page / 7 / mode / 1 up (accessed 21 January 2018)" type="proceedings paper">Bowerbank, 1873</bibRefCitation>
